steps.html_instructions:
Head west on I-10 W toward Exit 22A
Entering New Mexico
Keep right at the fork to continue on I-25 N, follow signs for Las Cruces/Albuquerque
Take exit 203 for NM-6 toward Los Lunas

Turn left onto NM-6 W/Main St NW
Continue to follow NM-6 W
Turn left to merge onto I-40 W toward Grants
Take exit 20 toward Muñoz Blvd
Turn right onto US-491 N

Turn left to stay on US-491 N
Entering Colorado

Slight left onto US-491 N/S Broadway (signs for I-491)
Continue to follow US-491 N
Entering Utah

Turn right onto US-191 N/N Main St
Continue to follow US-191 N
Turn left to merge onto I-70 W
Take exit 157 to merge onto US-191 N/US-6 W toward Price/Salt Lake
Keep left to continue on US-6 W
Keep right at the fork, follow signs for I-15 N/Salt Lake City and merge onto I-15 N
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-15 N
Keep left at the fork to stay on I-15 N, follow signs for Interstate 15 N/Ogden

Keep left at the fork to continue on I-84, follow signs for Boise
Entering Idaho
Take the Interstate 84 W/US 30 W exit on the left toward Twin Falls

Merge onto I-84/U.S. 30 W
Continue to follow I-84
Take exit 54 for US-20/US-26/Broadway Ave toward City Center

Turn right onto US-20 W/US-26 W/S Broadway Ave
Continue to follow S Broadway Ave
Turn left onto E Front St
Slight right onto W Front St (signs for West Front Street)
Turn left onto S Americana Blvd
